{"tid":990972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙天降花盆　擊碎平治車尾玻璃","createTime":"2019-01-22T04:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T05:06:58.000Z","uid":199292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd245c3e94f819ccabd51e747ea1b56440fee1b8","tid":990972,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nT0jROv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnT0jROv.png&h=d6f1c184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙發生高空墜物案。昨晚（21日）11時許，黃大仙翠鳳街11號一個花盆從高處墜下，擊中一輛黑色平治私家車，車尾擋風玻璃碎裂，花盆損毀，泥土撒在私家車上。據悉，年約30歲的男車主將私家車停泊於上址，到附近消夜後發現座駕受損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190122/s00001/1548123296324/黃大仙天降花盆-擊碎平治車尾玻璃\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190122%2Fs00001%2F1548123296324%2F%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%8D%E8%8A%B1%E7%9B%86-%E6%93%8A%E7%A2%8E%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83&d=v7jNhCDNvRQ0Kgdfj4AgnE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4618de6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190122%2Fs00001%2F1548123296324%2F%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%8D%E8%8A%B1%E7%9B%86-%E6%93%8A%E7%A2%8E%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83&h=a5158842\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190122/s00001/1548123296324/黃大仙天降花盆-擊碎平治車尾玻璃</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ec5e30afae3343e2ab325c5c5979fb984a3244","tid":990972,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e646fa5af11b54fdc6c77a9be0722a72fc08516","tid":990972,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已